---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="New Chapter: Starting as a postdoc at ITU" 
  description="Beginning my postdoc journey at the IT University of Copenhagen"
  ogImage="/itu.webp"
>
  <section class="mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-4">New Chapter: Starting as a postdoc at ITU</h1>
    <p class="opacity-60 mb-6">
      Beginning my postdoc journey at the IT University of Copenhagen
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex gap-4 mb-6">
      <img 
        src="/willem-logo.webp" 
        alt="Willem van der Maden" 
        class="w-[40px] aspect-square object-cover rounded-full" 
        width="40" 
        height="40" 
        loading="lazy" 
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div>
        <p class="font-medium">Willem van der Maden</p>
        <p class="opacity-60">
          1/15/2024 · 1 min read
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <article class="prose prose-invert">
      <p>I'm excited to announce that I've started a new position as a postdoctoral researcher at the IT University of Copenhagen!</p>
      
      <p>This new role offers fantastic opportunities to continue my research on AI, design, and human-computer interaction. I'm looking forward to collaborating with the amazing team at ITU and contributing to cutting-edge research in this vibrant academic community.</p>
      
      <p>Copenhagen has been welcoming, and I'm eager to see what discoveries and innovations lie ahead in this new chapter of my academic journey.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>